videos.description: Justin Jenifer knocks down a 3-pointer after an offensive rebound for the Bearcats.
videos.headline: Cincinnati 's Jenifer drains triple

videos.description: Abdul Ado blocks it on one end and Quinndary Weatherspoon finishes in transition with a dunk for the Bulldogs.
videos.headline: MSU's Ado block turns into a transition slam

videos.description: Aric Holman knocks down a 3-pointer after it bounces on the rim a few times.
videos.headline: MSU's Holman gets lucky bounce on 3-pointer

videos.description: Aric Holman throws down a thunderous jam before the first-half buzzer sounds for Mississippi State.
videos.headline: Holman ends the first half with power dunk

videos.description: Gary Clark finishes in transition with a huge alley-oop slam for Cincinnati.
videos.headline: Clark throws down the alley-oop

videos.description: Nick Weatherspoon creates a turnover and finishes on the other end with a layup for the Bulldogs.
videos.headline: MSU's Weatherspoon gets steal and layup
